<h3>Precipitation</h3>
<br><br>
Precipitation in November was in most of Europe much or exceptionally much below average (figure 11). Only in Scandinavia and in Spain precipitation was above average. In parts of northern Italy and southeastern Europe there was (almost) no precipitation at all.
