<h3>Radiation and Cloudiness</h3>
<br><br>
Global radiation and incoming shortwave radiation in November were around the long-term average in most of Europe (figures 13 and 14). In France and Spain and parts of central and eastern Europe the solar radiation was above average. Particularly in these regions cloud cover was, in correspondence with the map of solar radiation, below average (figure 15).
